From robert.castelo at upf.edu  Wed Jun 10 22:17:37 2015
From: robert.castelo at upf.edu (Robert Castelo)
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2015 22:17:37 +0200
Subject: [Bioc-devel] VRanges-class positive strandness and
