Dear Dan,

I am talking about the DOSE package, not GOSemSim.

FYI, I have figured out how to commit to Bioc svn via the following command:

git checkout devel
rm -rf .git/rebase-apply
git reset --hard 418b1dd
git svn rebase
git merge master --no-edit
git svn dcommit --add-author-from

see https://github.com/Bioconductor-mirror/DOSE/commits/master.

Thank you for your help and patience.

Best Regards,
Guangchuang



