 visible global function definition
In-Reply-To: <7d8ef61386d9a9eee347271544b947a6.squirrel@imap.ifi.lmu.de>
References: <7d8ef61386d9a9eee347271544b947a6.squirrel@imap.ifi.lmu.de>
